title: Purpose and Contribution
subtitle: The Three Essential Questions

Facilyn: The next topic, purpose and contribution, help you discover the meaning in what you're doing. There are three important questions that will guide you. 

Facilyn: If you're working within an organisation with a statement of purpose, you already thought about the answer to the first question. The other two help you find personal meaning in that larger purpose.

